, Lorcaserin, Diethylpropion, Mazindol', 'Entrectinib, Imatinib, Pralsetinib, Dabrafenib, Asciminib, Acalabrutinib, Dacomitinib, Pacritinib, Tepotinib, Fedratinib, Avapritinib, More', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/148253/', '[1] "Product Information. Zydelig (idelalisib)." Gilead Sciences, Foster City, CA.[2] "Product Information. Hivid (zalcitabine)." Roche Laboratories, Nutley, NJ.', 1767369485);
